import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-evaluacion-data', templateUrl: './evaluacion.component.html' }) export class EvaluacionComponent implements OnInit { public forecasts: WeatherForecast[] = []; public id: number = 0; constructor(private route: ActivatedRoute) { } ngOnInit() { this.id = Number(this.route.snapshot.paramMap.get('id')); } } interface WeatherForecast { date: string; temperatureC: number; temperatureF: number; summary: string; }
